Available Tools: get_stock_level | check_availability | get_low_stock_items | get_stock_by_location
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "sku": "string", "location_id": "string", "threshold": number }
Response Schema: { "sku": "string", "product_name": "string", "quantity": number, "location": "string", "status": "in_stock|low_stock|out_of_stock" }
---
Question: How many units of the wireless keyboard model KB-2024 do we have in the New York distribution center?
Call: { "func_call": "get_stock_level", "sku": "KB-2024-BLK", "location_id": "NYC-DC-01", "threshold": 50 }
Response: { "sku": "KB-2024-BLK", "product_name": "Wireless Ergonomic Keyboard", "quantity": 342, "location": "NYC-DC-01", "status": "in_stock" }

